title: Person of Interest   Behind the Scenes: Lady Killer
author: Spikey Unknown
comment: The show got better when Shaw was introduced. Than she had to leave because of pregnancy! Happy for Sarah,  but the show dipped in ratings   Thank God she came back for the 5th season!

Reese and Shaw were like a brother and sister fit to deal with all types of tough situations with both aggression and precision, together they were the batman and robin of person of interest. The nickname mayhem twins was the very best way to describe them, since they were practically unstoppable!!!
"are reese and shaw going to hook up?" more like root and shaw!

"We have a big, dark story to tell."

Carter die. Ha ha.
I wasn't ready for something that dark....
hate this show ended. loved root and shaw. shaw was my fav
